data.value: The Emenski Canyon Eco Path is one of the first eco path in Bulgaria. It is located near the village of Emen, Pavlikeni Municipality. The starting point of the eco path is the village of Emen, then it reaches first to the Emen cave. As they continue, unique views of the Canyon of Emen are seen. After the canyon comes the Negovanka Dam. The eco path offers a pleasant walk in the nature.
